The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to solve algebraic word problems. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves program induction and learning, which are common topics in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of rationales to generate explanations for the solutions also suggests that the paper could belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category, which deals with human-robot interaction and natural language processing. Finally, the paper could also be relevant to Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category, as it involves processing and understanding natural language descriptions of visual problems.
